
About
=====

ansicolor version 1.0.0  Copyright (C) 1999 Jamie Moyers

ansicolor provides a set of ostream manipulators for emitting the escape
codes used to display colored text on terminals that support it.

The test program "colortest" takes an optional argument to disable the
manipulators:

   colortest [no]



Author
======

   Jamie Moyers <jmoyers@geeks.com>


